column1: Bosscat Kitchen & Libations////We came here for happy hour
column2: and the food was delicious. We had the gulf tuna wraps and the gold medal chicken sandwich. The gulf tuna wraps on happy hour came with 2 wraps for $5. The full order on the menu was 4 for $12 so I just ordered 2 HH orders for $10! If you check in at this location
column3: you also get 10% off your order. I could see this restaurant being a tad pricey for dinner. But if you come for lunch/happy hour
column4: there are some pretty reasonable prices.
